        {
            "id": "https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/melting-memories.html",
            "url": "https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/melting-memories.html",
            "title": "Melting Memories",
            "summary": "I feel memories are out of my control. I cannot remember something I want to keep nor can I erase some moments I&hellip;",
            "content_html": "\n  <p>\n    I feel memories are out of my control. I cannot remember something I want to keep nor can I erase some moments I don’t want to remember at all. I often try to hold remnants of old memories, but it is impossible. I emotionally struggle with this experience. But, I realize that every moment of struggle is my life as well. Little by little, I learn how to harmonize with my past.\n  </p>\n\n  <div  class=\"gallery-wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"gallery\" data-columns=\"3\">\n      <figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/13/gallery/MeltingMemories_Lee-5.jpg\" data-size=\"4000x6000\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/13/gallery/MeltingMemories_Lee-5-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"1080\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/13/gallery/MeltingMemories_06.jpg\" data-size=\"3429x5143\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/13/gallery/MeltingMemories_06-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"1080\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/13/gallery/DSC00625.jpg\" data-size=\"6000x4000\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/13/gallery/DSC00625-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"480\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/13/gallery/DSC00617.jpg\" data-size=\"6000x4000\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/13/gallery/DSC00617-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"480\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/13/gallery/MeltingMemories_Lee_detail_1.jpg\" data-size=\"5143x3429\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/13/gallery/MeltingMemories_Lee_detail_1-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"480\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/13/gallery/MeltingMemories_Lee_detail_3.jpg\" data-size=\"4000x6000\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tinkermeer.github.io/sungjilee.github.io/media/posts/13/gallery/MeltingMemories_Lee_detail_3-thumbnail.jpg\" height=\"1080\" width=\"720\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure>\n    </div>\n  </div>",
